name: Air Strife One
description: "For what most would consider a suicide mission, for you it's just another special operation. "One plane, One Base." command says before they ship you off deep into enemy territory heavens knows how you'll come back in one piece. The stakes are high and so is your impatience. Good luck out there, pilot. I know you don't need it but I'll rest easier dropping you off alone out there." - The Adjutant
